  Ãƒâ€žÃƒâ€žÃƒâ€žÃƒâ€žÃƒâ€žÃƒâ€žÃƒâ€žÃƒâ€žÃƒâ€ž

  In War for the Overworld you have the power to create vast dungeons filled
  with hordes of evil minions who share a common goal: to crush the bones of
  the goodly heroes  that dare to enter  your  unhallowed  halls.  You  will
  command mighty armies, create  vicious  traps and cast dastardly spells to
  overcome the pitifully gallant armies that  defend foolish principles such
  as "honour" and "righteousness" - it's going  to  be  more fun than taking
  candy from a baby.

  Explore the options to the right to learn  what powers  you  command,  and
  learn what your enemy has in store for you.
